Everbread,s,Haystack,provides,online,travel,agencies,as,well,as,travel,meta,search,websites,with,a,highly,customizable,airfare,shopping,engine,and,multi,source,data,solution,tool,The,Haystack,miniAPI,offers,a,streamlined,method,for,utilizing,Haystack,You,can,build,widgets,extensions,websites,and,other,tools,to,display,content,from,Haystack,s,data,feeds,which,include,low,cost,and,traditional,airline,carriers,You,can,also,receive,up,to,free,API,calls,per,day,The,miniAPI,does,not,allow,you,to,book,results,The,miniAPI,utilizes,a,JSON,RPC,protocol,and,returns,are,formatted,in,JSON